de.tudresden.inf.rn.mobilis.sea.jingle.connection.manager

Class RawMediaManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jivesoftware.smackx.jingle.media.JingleMediaManager
      • de.tudresden.inf.rn.mobilis.sea.jingle.connection.manager.RawMediaManager

  • public class RawMediaManager
extends org.jivesoftware.smackx.jingle.media.JingleMediaManager
    This RawMediaManager is a concrete JingleMediaManager to create RawMediaSessions for all payloads of type 42 ("raw"). Due to an auxiliary SessionObserver it is also capable to lazy add ReceptionListeners and Raw media types
